Class WindowDataImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jguiraffe.gui.platform.swing.builder.window.WindowDataImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.sf.jguiraffe.gui.builder.window.WindowData
    public class WindowDataImpl
extends Object
implements net.sf.jguiraffe.gui.builder.window.WindowData
    An implementation of the WindowData interface that can be used for testing. For all properties required by the interface getter and setter methods are defined.

      • checkWindow

        public void checkWindow​(net.sf.jguiraffe.gui.builder.window.Window window)
        Checks if the properties of the given window match the data specified in this object. If this is not the case, an assertion failed error will be thrown.
        Parameters:
        window - the window to check
